title: Who, The - Who's Next [FLAC+MP3](Big Papi)
description:
[i]Holy moly. One can read all sorts of chats about which CD mastered version of this album is best. People will even drop $30-50 on a certain mastered CD. 

Big Papi does include CD catalog info now and then but is thinking about just including magic numbers from here on out.

The magic number is the DIDY typically printed on the inner hub of the disc. For example, This CD is MCA Records MCA-37217 with DIDY 1530. The DIDY number is more specific than the MCA number.

Anyway, I hope you enjoy this upload. That first track was my....errrrrr.....Big Papi's anthem as a teen.

- Big Papi[/i]
